plyTime":"2019-09-30T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"用條爛命幫大家行出黎架啲消息<br />\n唔該幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n軍營樓重解放軍 千真萬確<br />\n講大話我死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84851de6e100f66a4afc8f603c1f864b02d1fdf","tid":1607232,"uid":140432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:10:05.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"2540868dc59763848a3c30d8e7d314618e17a6f2","tid":1607232,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:11:33.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"4b868290853ec647e86c4d062ee16253a2937a6e","tid":1607232,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"啱啱係西環玩完<br />\n準備訓"},{"pid":"6d3bbfa1641c0c15f323bba01ea8f0f9148e8050","tid":1607232,"uid":63912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n港島撚"},{"pid":"bf3b644c2bc78b202fc4d8125dc7965beace6213","tid":1607232,"uid":98425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:19:13.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n<br />\n勿忘李卓人和理非遊行路線呀"},{"pid":"994636f7b88e06b5cfedcf71af0eb37f158bc092","tid":1607232,"uid":67479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb534989cff5872eb57389e668b9d0bb01a65128","tid":1607232,"uid":106565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:25:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b48c25e280b89c5ffb59bcbae221437c728e3c7","tid":1607232,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b868290853ec647e86c4d062ee16253a2937a6e","tid":1607232,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"啱啱係西環玩完<br />\n準備訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T19:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ee53dd7e366fa9d87538878e7de8aeddbc47f5","tid":1607232,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:03:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b55805e17c21fdee523005d11b41721e9387f7a1","tid":1607232,"uid":288786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:06:52.000Z","msg":"又跟民權抗爭老將的法國朋友聊天，當然論及香港的反送中運動，朋友說，看到香港警察一身造價不菲的裝備，頭部更用非常堅固的頭盔完全包裹，鐵甲人一樣，非常安全，但他說，非常奇怪，香港的抗爭者竟然不會向這些防暴警頭盔的保護鏡投擲任何顏料，個個防暴警的頭盔保護鏡竟然一塵不染。他說，投擲顏料相當容易，而保護鏡一旦看不清，就要把保護鏡拉起，甚至要卸下頭盔，自衛能力就大減，或要以真面目示人。"},{"pid":"ad4d5d1c369b29bd71aa04ed1d29d078834f3775","tid":1607232,"uid":32059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\npush"},{"pid":"d5fe5cdfc7e1be1b3afececa9c5a2460825e1aed","tid":1607232,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:17:43.000Z","msg":"我住港島都煩緊點樣返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗早少少退場會容易走啲"},{"pid":"ce7f0f8b093c6bc293d2e7b311fddb48e513182b","tid":1607232,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5fe5cdfc7e1be1b3afececa9c5a2460825e1aed","tid":1607232,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:17:43.000Z","msg":"我住港島都煩緊點樣返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗早少少退場會容易走啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:20:28.000Z","msg":"屌 我住正中聯辦個邊,真係唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次都有一大隊防暴係樓下等"},{"pid":"b91be72aa68b02e22e3d4b4239aaf1f9037b81d3","tid":1607232,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:23:21.000Z","msg":"南區撚返屋企都成問題"},{"pid":"0a33462286618c07edf3a75f76bf84afe4738eb2","tid":1607232,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4d5d1c369b29bd71aa04e